reviews.text: Great tasting food at affordable price. We were a party of 21 pax that turned up an hour before closing. The staff was surprised at this late turnout, but they did their best to ensure that the food came out quickly. Quality was not compromised. Good variety of choices on the menu and of very decent quality. Will go back again if I’m in the area
Their food are quite delicious. We tried their curry with roti (which was made fresh) and the laksa. Also, the restaurant has quite a beautiful view.
Not bad. Average taste as Thai dishes(which cannot go wrong, for me personally)

reviews.text: Lots of different stores in this mall. There are a lot of restaurants to choose from. Other than that, this mall is basically connected with the MTR station, so it's very convenient. I often come here. 😀
A big and comprehensive mall with various brands of clothing and shoes as well as many restaurants for meals. It is located at MTR  Yau Tong Station. Good for shopping

Domain Mall is the eight storey shopping mall in which has plenty of restaurants for different dining favor, as well as various retail shops. You can find fashion and accessories, convenience store, department store, beauty and health care, electric shop,..
The location in Yau Tong is easy to access. It opens from 7:00am to 11:00pm.

Lots of shops & restaurants 
Good place to view sunset
